so I am cobbling together

11:00.605 --> 11:02.906
a banner from
all the other discarded banners.

11:02.940 --> 11:06.126
"Second chunce four Lesle!

11:06.177 --> 11:10.247
"Perv Dexxxhrt equals...

11:10.281 --> 11:12.215
- birthday mouse"?
- Rat!

11:12.250 --> 11:13.950
Well, that's the closest thing
I could get to a rat.

11:13.968 --> 11:15.802
[Scoffs]
Leslie, listen to yourself.

11:15.853 --> 11:18.822
Loopholes,
scorched-earth policies.

11:18.856 --> 11:20.207
This isn't you.

11:20.241 --> 11:22.158
