supporting me on this!

11:22.176 --> 11:24.861
Dexhart has a sex scandal
the same day I'm leaving office?

11:24.896 --> 11:26.613
That is not a coincidence.

11:26.647 --> 11:27.664
This was meant to be.

11:27.698 --> 11:28.748
You know what?

11:28.800 --> 11:30.333
Why don't we gather everyone
in here,

11:30.367 --> 11:32.552
