if we had a boy.

11:38.075 --> 11:40.510
I have perfected the art
of shaving the human face.

11:40.544 --> 11:42.479
And I would love to be able
to pass that on.

11:42.513 --> 11:44.865
Toy trucks?
Superhero costumes?

11:44.899 --> 11:46.950
Tiny little acorn penis?
Forget it.

11:46.984 --> 11:48.151
A weird image.

11:48.169 --> 11:50.370
But one that does not diminish
my enthusiasm.

11:50.404 --> 11:52.222
Well, Ann Perkins,

11:52.256 --> 11:54.090
are you ready to find out
the sex of our baby?

11:54.108 --> 11:55.992
[Clink]
I'm ready.

11:56.027 --> 11:58.094
We are having a...

11:58.129 --> 12:00.647
"distributions."

12:00.681 --> 12:02.298
That's what it looks like:
Distributions.

12:02.316 --> 12:03.700
Let me see that.

12:03.734 --> 12:05.919
It says "congratulations,"
I think.

12:05.953 --> 12:07.036
Then it says,

12:07.054 --> 12:09.089
"I...leg smurf."

12:09.140 --> 12:10.257
Are we having a smurf?

12:10.308 --> 12:13.527
