more stressed out.

12:28.159 --> 12:29.826
Oh, good! You guys are here!

12:29.861 --> 12:31.561
Okay, everybody gather around.
I have a big announcement.

12:31.596 --> 12:34.064
I am officially
seeking reelection

12:34.098 --> 12:35.448
to the Pawnee City Council.

12:35.483 --> 12:37.584
I am gonna be running
for Dexhart's seat.

12:37.618 --> 12:41.504
And the campaign starts now.

12:41.538 --> 12:44.474
Oh, I love the sound of silence

12:44.508 --> 12:46.092
before a big cheer.

12:46.143 --> 12:47.727
That's what's happening, right?

12:47.762 --> 12:49.062
Leslie, no offense.

12:49.096 --> 12:50.680
I've heard a lot
of bad ideas today.

12:50.714 --> 12:53.149
- This is the worst.
- April?

12:53.184 --> 12:55.402
I would love it if you ran
an insane campaign

12:55.436 --> 12:57.571
and basically turned
into the joker.

12:57.605 --> 12:59.689
But that means you probably
shouldn't do it.

12:59.723 --> 13:00.774
- Andy?
- I don't know, Leslie.

13:00.825 --> 13:02.158
It seems risky.

13:02.193 --> 13:04.354
And I'd hate to see you
go through another tough fight.

13:04.362 --> 13:05.779
But I could be wrong.

13:05.830 --> 13:07.080
I haven't pooped in three days.

13:07.114 --> 13:09.799
Okay, Ron, you have always
given me sage counsel.

13:09.833 --> 13:11.801
And your words
carry great influence so...

13:11.835 --> 13:13.136
what do you think I should do?

13:13.170 --> 13:14.854
I do not think
you should run again.

13:14.889 --> 13:16.250
What the hell do you know,
Dum-Dum?

13:16.274 --> 13:18.725
All of you! Look,
this is my only option.

13:18.776 --> 13:20.477
I am running again
with or without you.

13:20.511 --> 13:22.779
Leslie, you're running
for office again?

13:22.813 --> 13:24.230
What a great idea!

13:24.282 --> 13:25.482
How can I help?

13:25.516 --> 13:26.750
Ugh...

13:29.275 --> 13:31.501
Well, no one else brought
me good business ideas.

13:31.621 --> 13:33.334
So I decided to
take care of it myself.

13:34.733 --> 13:35.850
Talking tissue!

13:35.884 --> 13:36.924
Any time you pull one out,

13:36.968 --> 13:38.502
