to hype you up.

13:38.520 --> 13:40.070
[Tom's voice]
Blow that nose, playah!

13:40.105 --> 13:41.271
No.

13:41.289 --> 13:43.290
[Sighs] This stinks.

13:43.341 --> 13:44.925
I'm just gonna have to go back
to my same job

13:44.960 --> 13:46.277
that I've had forever.

13:46.311 --> 13:47.745
Yeah, I get
why you're bummed out.

13:47.779 --> 13:48.779
I mean, look at me.

13:48.813 --> 13:50.447
I'm younger than you,

13:50.482 --> 13:51.715
and I already have
my own department.

13:51.750 --> 13:54.068
Plus I'm married,
and I make more money than you.

13:54.119 --> 13:55.469
Whatever. You just merged
your department with parks

13:55.503 --> 13:56.954
then made up your own title.

13:56.972 --> 13:58.088
[Snickering] Yeah.

13:58.106 --> 13:59.556
It's awesome.

13:59.574 --> 14:00.574
[Tom's voice] I'm empty, yo.

14:00.609 --> 14:03.878
Fill me up.

14:03.929 --> 14:05.963
Do that again.

14:05.997 --> 14:08.332
[Knock on door]

14:08.366 --> 14:11.602
What could you possibly need
at 6:00 in the morning?

14:11.636 --> 14:12.916
We couldn't read your writing,

14:12.938 --> 14:14.499
and we need
to know the sex of our baby.

14:14.522 --> 14:16.790
I'm watching cartoons
with my son.

14:16.825 --> 14:17.892
Daddy!

14:17.926 --> 14:19.543
An Elmer Fudd one is on!

14:19.561 --> 14:21.262
Stop it.
Hey, what's up, beautiful?

14:21.296 --> 14:23.080
Jean-Ralphio.
I live in the guesthouse.

14:23.114 --> 14:24.381
What do you say
you and I get together

14:24.416 --> 14:25.849
