14:25.884 --> 14:26.901
I-I'm pregnant.

14:26.935 --> 14:28.535
- The more the merrier.
- With my baby.

14:28.570 --> 14:29.670
Well, you can come too,
beautiful.

14:29.704 --> 14:30.888
Look at that.

14:30.922 --> 14:33.090
I guess sometimes
I call men "beautiful" too.

14:33.108 --> 14:36.577
I guess I'm
[Singing] open-minded as hell.

14:36.628 --> 14:38.762
And I think
you're pretty good-looking.

14:38.797 --> 14:40.237
- Thank you.
- Can you just read that

14:40.265 --> 14:41.732
and tell us
what the sex is, please?

14:41.766 --> 14:42.933
Wow.

14:42.951 --> 14:44.234
It looks like
the chicken that wrote this

14:44.252 --> 14:45.753
had a stroke on the paper.

14:45.804 --> 14:46.887
[Laughter]

14:46.938 --> 14:48.689
Listen, I-I kind of remember.

14:48.740 --> 14:50.124
But I don't want to say
anything that's wrong.

14:50.158 --> 14:51.659
Give me 15 minutes.

14:51.710 --> 14:52.927
I will get dressed.

14:52.978 --> 14:54.895
We'll go down
to my office. Okay.

14:54.930 --> 14:56.697
Well, have a good day
at work today, daddy.

14:56.731 --> 14:58.232
Also,
if you don't know already,

14:58.266 --> 15:00.050
