18:11.025 --> 18:12.659
Uh-oh. Oh, time's up.

18:12.694 --> 18:14.644
Okay, if you want
to keep talking,

18:14.662 --> 18:15.996
you're gonna have to pay me
1,200 more dollars.

18:16.030 --> 18:18.081
- I just need--
- No, I swear to God,

18:18.116 --> 18:20.584
if you say one more word,
you will legally owe me $1,200,

18:20.618 --> 18:22.986
and I will sue you.
Let's not end it like that.

18:23.004 --> 18:24.755
Okay, great to see you, Leslie.

18:24.789 --> 18:26.039
Those five words are on me.

18:26.090 --> 18:28.258
Should I move this back?
Don't answer it!

18:29.257 --> 18:30.327
I don't know
what you're thinking,

18:30.345 --> 18:34.014
but you have a press conference
in ten minutes.

18:36.212 --> 18:37.689
Well, this is it...

18:37.929 --> 18:39.231
The final moment..

18:39.615 --> 18:41.005
What are you hoping for?

18:41.526 --> 18:44.070
I will honestly be happy
either way.

18:44.192 --> 18:45.226
Me too.

18:45.260 --> 18:47.061
Boy or girl,

18:47.095 --> 18:48.395
it doesn't matter.

18:48.429 --> 18:50.481
Because it will literally be

18:50.532 --> 18:52.616
the greatest child
who's ever lived.

18:52.651 --> 18:54.902
You swear you have
no preference?

18:54.936 --> 18:55.953
You?

18:55.987 --> 18:58.706
Not at all.

18:58.740 --> 19:00.824
Who's ready? Raise your hand.

19:00.876 --> 19:03.210
It's a boy!
Both: Yes!

19:03.245 --> 19:04.662
