a preference.

19:04.713 --> 19:06.547
I didn't. I just really
wanted it to be a boy.

19:06.581 --> 19:07.581
Me too.

19:07.615 --> 19:09.333
I don't know why.

19:09.384 --> 19:10.801
You guys are just so neat.

19:10.835 --> 19:13.120
Would you be interested
