about my future.

19:28.737 --> 19:32.940
I will be heading to lunch today
with my husband.

19:32.974 --> 19:34.441
At JJ's diner.

19:34.475 --> 19:36.777
We will eat waffles.

19:36.811 --> 19:38.662
And then we will go home
and make out on our couch.

19:38.697 --> 19:40.331
That is my future.

19:40.365 --> 19:43.951
For now.

19:43.985 --> 19:48.372
It's been an honor
to serve this town.

19:48.423 --> 19:51.175
And I will cherish the memories
forever.

19:51.209 --> 19:53.093
Thank you.

19:53.128 --> 19:54.712
- Ms. Knope!
- There you have it.

19:54.763 --> 19:56.931
A shockingly unshocking
press conference

19:56.965 --> 19:58.682
